I have successfully canceled the premium membership subscription on the shopping website. I completed the following steps:

1. Clicked on the 'Account' button in the navigation bar
2. Clicked on the Premium Member information box
3. Clicked on 'Cancel Membership' button

7. Clicked on 'Next Step' to proceed
8. Confirmed my final decision to cancel despite the warning about eligibility reassessment
